{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act33side_level_act33side_10_end","storyGroup":"act33side","storySort":18,"storyDependence":"act33side_level_act33side_10_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BB-10","storyName":"再见，再见","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"一切都已尘埃落定，凯尔希赶回巴别塔时已经无力回天。特蕾西娅借已经戴上黑王冠的阿米娅之口向凯尔希阐述了最后的理想。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act33side/level_act33side_10_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act33side_10","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":20,"next":22,"characters":["特蕾西娅","凯尔希","？？？","“阿米娅”","特雷西斯","阿斯卡纶","Ace","Mantra","Pith","Scout","Logos","孽茨雷","杜卡雷","W"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"charslot","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_desolate_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_49_i21_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.15","yScale":"1.15","fadetime":"0","id":7},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.15","yScaleFrom":"1.15","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"20","block":"false","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅拉着眼前之人的手，就像他们的第一次见面。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"她静静与那双眼睛对视，看到其中不停变换着情绪，最终，只留下空洞一片。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"她知道，最后的记忆已经抹去，灵魂已经纯净。","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你的记忆已经死去，你的灵魂会重生......","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"真是可怕的伎俩......","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"可那些人低估了你的善良，低估了你对胜利的渴望。那些人低估了我们，低估了泰拉坚忍至今的起源。","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"博士，姑且再让我最后一次如此称呼你......","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这是我对你小小的报复。","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"也是我对你......最后的馈赠。","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"记忆从不塑造你自己。以你最本来的面目......","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......重新生活在......大地之上吧。去看看这个世界，去感受生活的喜怒哀乐，去结识形形色色的泰拉人民......","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"也许......你的旅程会从苦难中开始，总是离不开这片大地昏沉的月影，可你总能......见到太阳升起。","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"然后，我相信，你会重新得出一个答案。得出真正属于你的答案。","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"那一定......和凯尔希，和我曾听到的那段呢喃一样......","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"令人热泪盈眶吧。","id":25},{"type":"dialog","id":26},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":27},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"image","id":29},{"type":"charslot","id":30},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_49_g10_theresaoffice.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":31},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":32},{"type":"bg","id":33,"from":"0","to":"1","duration":"3","block":"false"},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":34},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"生命在流逝。","id":36},{"type":"text","text":"她的耳边逐渐响起了来自远方的挽歌。对了，菈玛莲曾与她设下连接。","id":37},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅自己的气息在逐渐微弱......但她也感受到了前所未有的轻松。","id":38},{"type":"text","text":"她尽力将阿米娅护在怀中，保护着。阿米娅的心跳令她安心。","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我......我有点累了，捧住那顶冠冕真的很累。","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"累了就得休息，对吧，阿米娅？","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我曾想过......","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"也许有天......我们会一起让这片大地上的每一个人，都能平静入梦。","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"虽然很遥远，但也许，你会替我看到那一天......","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"阿米娅，当你醒来......","id":45},{"type":"dialog","id":46},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":47},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"background","id":49},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_femalebreathesoft","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"fe","id":50},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"fe","fadetime":"2","id":51},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_49_i01.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","fadetime":"0","id":52},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.05","yScaleFrom":"1.05","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"20","block":"false","id":53},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......你就要继续前行。","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"呼——好累......","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"不，她还没有来......","id":57},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","channel":"fe","fadetime":"2","id":58},{"type":"text","text":"她只有最后一丝珍贵的力气了。","id":59},{"type":"text","text":"她有必须要等的人。","id":60},{"type":"text","text":"万幸，她已经听到了那人赶来的声音。","id":61},{"type":"dialog","id":62},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":63},{"type":"text","text":"终于，哪怕无力再睁开眼，但她也知道——","id":64},{"type":"text","text":"那人回来了——","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"凯尔希......","id":66},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"fe","fadetime":"2","id":67},{"type":"text","text":"凯尔希。","id":68},{"type":"dialog","id":69},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":70},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":71},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"image","id":73},{"type":"bg","id":74,"from":"1","to":"0","duration":"0.1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":75},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_49_g10_theresaoffice.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":76},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"r","id":78},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"r","fadetime":"1.5","id":79},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#9$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"特蕾西娅......","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿米娅......博士......","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#8$1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我明知道这样的可能性始终存在......为什么......","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我应该留下，是我......","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#9$1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"特蕾......西娅。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我......我们本可以......","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":92},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#8$1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"特蕾西娅......确认死......死亡。","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"Mon3tr，听我命令......","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"准备......应对后续的袭击。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博士和阿米娅......不能再出事......不能！","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#7$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"Mon3tr——！","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"凯尔希......","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"凯尔希。","id":104},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#4$1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——！","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":107},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"charslot","id":111},{"type":"background","id":112},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_49_i18.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅睁开了眼，瞳孔中隐隐现出粉色的菱形。","id":115},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅依旧紧闭双眼。","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"但凯尔希知道。","id":117},{"type":"text","text":"这就是她。","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"凯尔希......我一直在等你。","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"特蕾西娅！我——","id":120},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"6","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"没事的，没事的，凯尔希。","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"听我说——","id":123},{"type":"dialog","id":124},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"charslot","id":127},{"type":"background","id":128},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_49_i13.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":129},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"20","block":"false","id":130},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magicrelievey","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"ma","id":131},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.8","channel":"ma","fadetime":"2","id":132},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"我已经死去。","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"你现在看到的，是我寄留于王冠中的意识，借由这个孩子的身体与你告别。","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"凯尔希，告诉我，你是否将那面巴别塔旗帜升上了卡兹戴尔的天空？","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我将它送回卡兹戴尔了，我看着它升上了高空......","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"谢谢。","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我回来得太晚了，我明知道有这种可能......","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"不要为此自责，凯尔希，你有自己的任务需要完成。","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"而且在最后......我还是等到你了，这已经足够。","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......我们，没有更多时间告别了吗？","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"对不起，凯尔希......","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......我明白。","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"请不要责怪自己，凯尔希。","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"我们曾信任过博士，我希望你能在未来继续沿着我们的道路前进。","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"凯尔希，不必再为此而疑虑。","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"我杀死了他，也救下了他。","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"请将他送回他应在的地方，如果他还能醒来......","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"指引他，他会带领我们走到我们道路的终点——","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"我深信不疑。","id":152},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"ma","fadetime":"2","id":154},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"charslot","id":157},{"type":"image","id":158},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_49_g10_theresaoffice.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":159},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":160},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#11$1","id":161},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#4$1","id":162},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":163},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":164},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":165},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我知道了。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"但......我们不能再冒险进入......罗德岛的深处。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我会拜托一位熟人，将博士送到乌萨斯。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"在切尔诺伯格，他会被安置得很好。博士继续留在罗德岛，风险......太高。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/25/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"这样很好......凯尔希。那以后的事情，就要交给阿米娅了。","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"她会走上一条很难的路。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我会陪着她，巴别塔......会陪着她。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"她很幼小，但足够坚强。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"凯尔希，我并非因为临时起意才自私地将王冠留在巴别塔......留给她。","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"想要打破循环，应对即将到来的未来......魔王不能只是萨卡兹的魔王，魔王也不能成为泰拉的魔王。","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"魔王不是枷锁，不是统御，也不是无可匹敌的力量。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"魔王是钥匙，是......“文明的存续”。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"不要告诉阿米娅，凯尔希，她也不必现在就承担这一切。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"踏上那条道路之后，她会明白，她也需要明白——","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"唯有战胜所有的阻力，才能找到那扇通向大地的门。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你呢？","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1295_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"我将会消失在理想之中，而她......","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"她会成为燃尽所有腐朽的火焰。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1295_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":191},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"ma","fadetime":"2","id":192},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":193},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"charslot","id":195},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_bg_bg_victoria.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":196},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":197},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“新的战争即将开启......凯尔希。","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":199},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“特雷西斯，我的血亲......","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":200},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“他会在维多利亚降临属于我们的摇篮，源石会铺满那片土地......”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":201},{"type":"subtitle","id":202},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","id":203},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#6$1","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"她将要离去。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":206},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":207},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“他会给大地上的其他种族带去灾难......”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":209},{"type":"subtitle","id":210},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":211},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#4$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"而你们会是她所追寻理念的最后挣扎。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"最后的努力。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":217},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“他会让萨卡兹再次成为全泰拉的敌人。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":218},{"type":"subtitle","id":219},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#5$1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"刽子手们——","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"不要试图放弃，在她的结局既定之前......","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"向我证明，那条道路依旧有赢下未来的契机——","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":226},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":227},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“阻止那一天的到来，在一切都不可挽回之前......”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":228},{"type":"subtitle","id":229},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#4$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"向她证明，你们所坚持的和平依旧可以得到回应。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"但遗憾的是，我的同胞们......","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"偿还血债的呼声已经响彻在这片大地——","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":236},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":238},{"type":"curtain","direction":"6","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.38","fadetime":"4","id":239},{"type":"curtain","direction":"2","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.38","fadetime":"4","id":240},{"type":"background","id":241},{"type":"charslot","id":242},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_49_i12.png","screenadapt":"coverall","y":"250","xScale":"1.7","yScale":"1.7","fadetime":"0","id":243},{"type":"imagetween","yFrom":"150","yTo":"-100","duration":"20","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":244},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_wtchkgopenftstp","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"w","id":245},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"w","fadetime":"4","id":246},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“卡兹戴尔的仇恨不应该继续绵延。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":251},{"type":"subtitle","id":252},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"她的死亡已成定局。","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你们失去了一位魔王。","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我失去了唯一的亲人。","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"而我不会让一切牺牲毫无意义。","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"同胞们——","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"无论你们为了和平，或是为了复仇而聚集于此。","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我会听到你们的声音。","id":261},{"type":"dialog","id":262},{"type":"curtain","direction":"6","fillfrom":"0.38","fillto":"0","fadetime":"8","id":263},{"type":"curtain","direction":"2","fillfrom":"0.38","fillto":"0","fadetime":"8","id":264},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_49_i12.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"4","id":265},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"20","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":266},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“复仇。战争。生存。未来。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":269},{"type":"subtitle","id":270},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你们会看到萨卡兹真正的路在哪里。","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你们浸染维多利亚阶梯的鲜血终有归处——","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"这里，必须成为我们新的开始。","id":274},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我此刻依然能够听到萨卡兹人民中的声音，凯尔希......","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":278},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“当我离众魂越近，那些声音便越发清晰。","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":279},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我从万年的呐喊中所听到的是——”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":280},{"type":"subtitle","id":281},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"苦难会再次降临——","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"全泰拉的屈服——","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"会自此而起。","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"萨卡兹——","id":286},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“萨卡兹——”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":290},{"type":"subtitle","id":291},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"——将浴火重生。","id":293},{"type":"dialog","id":294},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“——将摧毁大地。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":297},{"type":"subtitle","id":298},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"image","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"我们需要阻止他，凯尔希。","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可是......现在的巴别塔做不到。","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"你总是会想出办法。","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“阿米娅”","text":"而且，在我们共同建立的巴别塔，你永远不是一个人——","id":304},{"type":"dialog","id":305},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/34/Avg_49_i16_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":306},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":307},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我们的同伴会帮助你。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":308},{"type":"subtitle","id":309},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"殿下——","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"特蕾西娅......！殿下......！殿下！","id":312},{"type":"dialog","id":313},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_openftstprun","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"o","id":314},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"o","fadetime":"3","id":315},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_49_i16_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":316},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":317},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":318},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“他们是最为坚定的人。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":320},{"type":"subtitle","id":321},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......殿下......","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"殿下，我回来了......","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"过去，我站在这里时，迎接我的总是你。","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"但这次......你不在。","id":326},{"type":"dialog","id":327},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你还能听到我的声音吗？","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"为什么不能再等等，殿下......","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......该死！该死！","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我要他们偿还......我向你保证。","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"所有参与的人......","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"哪怕是他......哪怕是——","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"老师......特雷西斯——","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"特雷西斯......","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"他必须面对我......我......必须面对他！","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"所有的背叛......痛苦......","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"特蕾西娅殿下......特雷西斯......","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我......我唯二的......我却......","id":340},{"type":"text","text":"云层遮住斜阳，阴影笼罩了阿斯卡纶。","id":341},{"type":"text","text":"她再无阳光。再无信仰。","id":342},{"type":"text","text":"她挣扎过了，她努力过了。","id":343},{"type":"text","text":"只有死亡属于风暴之子。","id":344},{"type":"dialog","id":345},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"image","id":348},{"type":"charslot","id":349},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_bg_49_g5_furnaceplatform.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":350},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_churchfire","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"c","id":351},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.3","channel":"c","fadetime":"2","id":352},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":353},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“他们是最为出色的人。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":355},{"type":"subtitle","id":356},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1309_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"......","id":359,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_1309_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1300_1#7$1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mantra","text":"......","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1300_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1310_1#1$1","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Pith","text":"......","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_1310_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1311_1#1$1","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"......Logos。","id":365,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/28/Avg_avg_npc_1311_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#1$1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"......嗯。","id":367,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#5$1","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"我们......我不知道......我们还是......","id":369,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1311_1#1$1","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"先撤退吧。","id":371,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/28/Avg_avg_npc_1311_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"先......回巴别塔去。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/28/Avg_avg_npc_1311_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":373},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"c","fadetime":"2","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"charslot","id":377},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_bg_bg_laccolith.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":378},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":379},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":380},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“他们更是毫不质疑我们理想的人。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":381},{"type":"subtitle","id":382},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":383},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_410_1#7$1","duration":"0.5","id":384},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_420_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":385},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":386},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_410_1#7$1","focus":"n","id":387},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_420_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"孽茨雷","text":"......","id":389,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_npc_420_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_410_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜卡雷","text":"......结束了。","id":391,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_410_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_420_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"孽茨雷","text":"为何......我竟会......？","id":393,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_npc_420_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_410_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜卡雷","text":"......我也正奇怪呢，食腐者之王。","id":395,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_410_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜卡雷","text":"我以为我早就习惯了魔王之死。","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_410_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":397},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":398},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":399},{"type":"charslot","id":400},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_bg_bg_barracks.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":401},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":402},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":403},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“他们——留下的人，都是无需怀疑背叛的人。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":404},{"type":"subtitle","id":405},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":406},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_046","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_avg_npc_046.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......不可能。","id":409,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_avg_npc_046.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"谁*萨卡兹粗口*负责的通讯频段？！是不是让军事委员会截了，开这种玩笑？！","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_avg_npc_046.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_ldrdhtgrnd","volume":"1","id":412},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"我不信......我......你给我闭嘴！Scout！","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_avg_npc_046.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"本舰......应该在这个方向！","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_avg_npc_046.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":416},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"特蕾西娅......怎么会这么容易就......就......死掉？！","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_avg_npc_046.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":419},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"4","id":420},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":422},{"type":"charslot","id":423},{"type":"background","id":424},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":425},{"type":"text","text":"898年冬，魔王死了。","id":426},{"type":"text","text":"以勒什死在了卡兹戴尔毁灭之前。","id":427},{"type":"text","text":"魂灵熔炉爆炸而扬起的粉尘在卡兹戴尔地区上空飘荡了三天三夜......","id":428},{"type":"text","text":"最终它们如黑色的雪花般落下。","id":429},{"type":"text","text":"埋葬了侵略者的尸骨。","id":430},{"type":"text","text":"也埋葬了那座曾名为“卡兹戴尔”的废墟。","id":431},{"type":"dialog","id":432},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_memory_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":433,"musicid":1},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_bg_bg_battlefield.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":434},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":435},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":436},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":437},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"卡兹戴尔......不复存在了。","id":439,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":440},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":441},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":442},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但卡兹戴尔从未消失。","id":444,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这是我从魔王那里听来的，他说，卡兹戴尔曾毁灭三千余次，但最终都会被重建。","id":445,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......说不定只是以勒什欺骗民众的把戏。","id":447,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"他已经死了，特雷西斯。","id":449,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"可即使那是他在宫殿中庸碌无事时编撰的故事......至少在这些故事里，我还能听到一丝向往。","id":450,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"对可能存在的，平稳生活的向往。","id":452,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"胜利了之后呢，如今大家又将在这片土地上开始流浪......","id":454,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"同胞们以英雄之名称颂我们，我们却只能还以一片了无生机的废墟。","id":455,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们又能做什么呢？","id":456,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"“英雄”......这场战争结束的那刻起，“英雄”便已毫无意义......","id":457,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"的确如此。","id":459,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"还有......从刚才开始，我似乎一直有听到众魂的耳语......","id":461,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"它们越发清晰了......","id":462,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"multiline","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我不知道众魂希望引导我去向何处......","id":463},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":464},{"type":"multiline","name":"特蕾西娅","end":"true","text":"你呢？","id":465},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......我也是。","id":467,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我本将这视作胜利时因兴奋而产生的虚妄......但看来，不止如此。","id":468,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"众魂在召唤你我。","id":470,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"那走吧，无论何处。","id":472,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":473},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":474},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","id":475},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":476},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":477},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":478},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":479},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":480},{"type":"charslot","id":481},{"type":"background","id":482},{"type":"text","text":"魔王以勒什长眠于此。","id":483},{"type":"text","text":"在山峦般堆砌的尸骸之下。","id":484},{"type":"text","text":"在更久远的将来，无人会知晓，曾有一位王陨落于此。","id":485},{"type":"text","text":"他如此平庸，如此普通。","id":486},{"type":"text","text":"萨卡兹从不铭记失败者。","id":487},{"type":"text","text":"在这场改变萨卡兹命运的战争中，人们只会记得六个无比耀眼的英雄之名。","id":488},{"type":"dialog","id":489},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":490},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":491},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_bg_bg_battlefield.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":492},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":493},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":494},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":495},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":496},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们到了。","id":497,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":498},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我记得这里......以勒什的车辇崩毁之后，我们在这里宣誓加入这场战争。","id":499,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":500},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"这是我们的起点......","id":501,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"一个衣匠，一个卫士。","id":502,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":503},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......你听到了吗，特雷西斯？","id":504,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"众魂的声音从我们的脚下传来......","id":505,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":506},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......啊。","id":507,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"是它呀。","id":508,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":509},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"是的。","id":510,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"原来，它这么渺小。","id":511,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":512},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":513},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":514},{"type":"charslot","id":515},{"type":"background","id":516},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_49_i14.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":517},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.5","yScaleTo":"1.5","duration":"60","block":"false","id":518},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":519},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":520},{"type":"text","text":"王冠。","id":521},{"type":"text","text":"在死亡的见证之下——","id":522},{"type":"text","text":"在众魂的见证之下——","id":523},{"type":"text","text":"双子共同举起了王冠。","id":524},{"type":"text","text":"王冠同时选择了双子。","id":525},{"type":"text","text":"废墟之上，不知是否真实存在的众魂，同时选定了两种希望。","id":526},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......由你来戴上这顶冠冕吧，特蕾西娅。","id":527},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"为何？","id":528},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"魔王不过是历史选择沉默时，属于可怜人的一厢情愿。","id":529},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"是啊......我们改变萨卡兹的命运，不需要借助一个既定的外力。","id":530},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但在这个绝望的时代，它会为我们的同胞带回一丝希望。","id":531},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我并不适合成为带来希望的那个人。","id":532},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我的剑会开辟前路。而你来为我们指引方向。","id":533},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......我明白了。","id":534},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"战争方才结束，这一次，我们又要肩负它到何时？","id":535},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"在重新找到安身的家园之前，在黑王冠的苦难将我们吞没之前......","id":536},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"在所有人能安然睡在同一片天空下之前。","id":537},{"type":"dialog","id":538},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":539},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你刚才提到了，“指引方向”，还记得我们以前那次冒险吗？","id":540},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你握着剑，背着我......","id":541},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"而你指引我从灌木中劈出回家的路。","id":542},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"特蕾西娅......","id":543},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"容我亲手为你戴冠。","id":544},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"好啊。","id":545},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"特雷西斯......","id":546},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我会向所有萨卡兹宣誓......","id":547},{"type":"dialog","id":548},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":549},{"type":"sticker","id":550,"text":"“我们永远平等。”","delay":"0.001","width":"800","x":"275","y":"330","duration":"3","alignment":"center","size":"24"},{"type":"sticker","id":551,"duration":"4","block":"false"},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":552},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":553},{"type":"charslot","id":554},{"type":"background","id":555},{"type":"image","id":556}],"characters":["特蕾西娅","凯尔希","？？？","“阿米娅”","特雷西斯","阿斯卡纶","Ace","Mantra","Pith","Scout","Logos","孽茨雷","杜卡雷","W"]}